{
  "texts": [
    "The author also demonstrated how integrating gene expression and DNA methylation data could improve prediction accuracy.",
    "In Basher et al. (2021), the authors have developed a technique to detect AD using structural magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) data that has been slice-wise volumetrically extracted from the left and right hippocampi.",
    "The suggested approach combines a convolutional neural network (CNN) model and a deep neural network (DNN) model.",
    "A two-stage ensemble, Hough-CNN, has been used to automatically locate the left and right hippocampi.",
    "Three-dimensional patches with 80 × 80 × 80 voxels are extracted using the localized hippocampus positions."
  ]
}